    sourceTier: "ai_assisted",
    sourceNotes:
      "Generated via AI-assisted analysis of Malachi 3:6-12. Draws on critical commentaries (Hill, Petersen, Glazier-McDonald) and storehouse tithe scholarship (Verhoef, Stuart). Prosperity gospel critique informed by Bowler's Blessed and scholarly analysis of televangelism's economic impact. Generosity research drawn from the Science of Generosity Initiative (University of Notre Dame)."
